description:
When this card inflicts battle damage to your opponent: You can activate 1 of these effects;
 Discard 1 random card from their hand.
 Send the top 2 cards of their Deck to the GY.

If you control a Dragon monster: Activate 1 of these effects;
 Inflict 800 damage to your opponent.
 Target 1 monster with 800 or less DEF; destroy that target.

Activate 1 of these effects;
 Gain 1200 LP.
 Inflict 800 damage to your opponent.
